  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;a id=&quot;XE_BRMS&quot; name=&quot;XE_BRMS&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial&quot;>S&lt;/span>&lt;/a>ystem designed to modify&#xD;
    and manage business logic independently from the enterprise application.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;BRMS provides a way to automate&#xD;
    decision making and execute precisely on business policy. Consequently, policies and decisions form the core of all&#xD;
    business processes and activities.&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; size=&quot;1&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font>A BRMS product&amp;nbsp;should include&#xD;
